    "(1) Overall Performance Comparison.",
    "GR methods generally outperform traditional sparse and dense retrieval approaches in most tasks.",
    "Notably, GENRE achieves the highest scores in several categories, including FEVER (0.847), AY2 (0.928), WnWi (0.877), and WnCw (0.706), outperforming the best sparse method BM25 and dense methods like MT-DPR.",
